  "limitations": [
    "Results are from one M4 Max and synthetic stress/hot workloads, not the full upstream dataset matrix.",
    "p10/p90 are observed sample dispersion, not confidence intervals.",
    "No privileged energy or temperature telemetry was collected.",
    "XGBoost allocates its returned output inside the timed call; Metal reuses caller output storage. XGBoost retains its DMatrix; Metal wraps or copies X each call.",
